-- Australia's High Court Clears Asylum Request Assessment, Review Says
-- B y   B e n   S h a r p l e s
-- 2010-11-11T20:33:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-11/australia-s-high-court-clears-asylum-request-assessment-review-says.html
Australia’s High Court has ruled
that people held in immigration detention on Christmas Island
off the country’s northwestern coast can have conclusions about
their application for asylum reviewed by the courts, the
Australian Financial Review reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
